        "WE’RE A LITTLE CHRISTIAN BAND"
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "chorus",
      "lines": [
        "1. Mpingo wa Akristu ’fe, tikondwra mwa Ambuye",
        "Tinka m’dziko labwino, tikondwera mwa Ambuye.",
        "CHORUS:",
        "Mpulumutsi, Mtitsogoze bwino bwino,",
        "Pakupita kunka mmwambamo.",
        "2. Timayenda bwinotu, tikondwera mwa Ambuye",
        "Tigonjetsa mdaniyo, tikondwera mwa Ambuye.",
        "3. Msanga tidzapumadi, tikondwera mwa Ambuye",
        "Tidzabvala kronayo, tikondwra mwa Ambuye."
      ]
    }
